才的发明被否定、求职屡屡碰壁，她迫切需要一条能改变人生的出口。此时，陷入舆论危机的帝国王室，将她视为挽救形象的最佳工具。就在欲望与绝望碰上的那一刻，一场披著「救赎」外衣的利用正式开始!","id":64566,"region":"日漫","slug":"http://manwatj.cc/book/468277","status":0,"status_text":"连载中","tags":["爱情"],"title":"以救赎之名的残酷","updated_at":"2026-03-11T15:11:11.581836+08:00","views":3},{"author":"JOGEN","category":"一般","cover_image":"","cover_local_path":"","cover_original_url":"https://mwfimsvfast27.cc/static/upload3/book/id/468278/cover_1.jpg?v=1773179887","created_at":"2026-03-11T06:30:42.592118+08:00","description":"曾为社畜的我穿越成为了游戏中的贵族角色，虽然偏偏是个未来将被反派杀害的支线路人，但是没关系！就让我用金钱的力量，好好教化这群还是小小孩的反派角色，并享受成为贵族的优渥待遇吧！ 皇天不负苦心人，在认真的栽培之下，他们全都成长为平凡的大人，然而我…却成了王国中的最终BOSS?!","id":64565,"region":"韩国","slug":"http://manwatj.cc/book/468278","status":0,"status_text":"连载中","tags":["冒险","奇幻"],"title":"成为反派恶角的赞助者","updated_at":"2026-03-11T15:11:08.203098+08:00","views":1},{"author":"ミサンガ (ミュシャ)","category":"禁漫","cover_image":"","cover_local_path":"","cover_original_url":"https://mwfimsvfast27.cc/static/upload3/book/content/20260311/c_2b0b2d1403056936caa84d9dc19d7ca4d.png","created_at":"2026-03-11T04:04:59.154613+08:00","description":"星铁全彩图","id":64564,"region":"日漫","slug":"http://manwatj.cc/book/468272","status":0,"status_text":"连载中","tags":["全彩","同人","CG杂图","C104","崩坏：星穹铁道","人偶","马尾","双马尾","比基尼"],"title":"『キミ』との旅","updated_at":"2026-03-11T08:57:49.240539+08:00","views":0},{"author":"skyzen","category":"禁漫","cover_image":"","cover_local_path":"","cover_original_url":"https://mwfimsvfast27.cc/static/upload3/book/content/20260311/c_241a96a2abc0fa77656b59a96dc451d92.png","created_at":"2026-03-11T04:04:52.190044+08:00","description":"孩子们我回来了","id":64563,"region":"日漫","slug":"http://manwatj.cc/book/468273","status":1,"status_text":"已完结","tags":["全彩","短篇","非人类"],"title":"僵尸娘 情侣篇后记一","updated_at":"2026-03-11T15:11:18.472056+08:00","views":5},{"author":"YOUMO","category":"禁漫","cover_image":"","cover_local_path":"","cover_original_url":"https://mwfimsvfast27.cc/static/upload3/book/content/20260311/c_29db2a